    <item>
      <title>Kokkos training</title>
      <link>https://cexa-project.org/news/2023-07-27-kokkos-training/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://cexa-project.org/news/2023-07-27-kokkos-training/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;CExA organises a 3-days Kokkos training from the 20 to the 22 of Septembre in
Saclay provided by Kokkos lead developers
&lt;a href=&#34;https://extremecomputingtraining.anl.gov/speakers/christian-trott-snl/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Cristian Trott&lt;/a&gt;
and
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ornl.gov/staff-profile/damien-t-lebrun-grandie&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Damien Lebrun-Grandié&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Registration to the first day is free and open to all, but mandatory to attend:
&lt;a href=&#34;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/e/kokkos-1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/e/kokkos-1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following two days will consist in practical work in the lab room and
registration is limited to 30 people, with priority given to CEA members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://goo.gl/maps/DrqiALxY547iXshJA&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Neurospin Amphitheatre&lt;/a&gt; for
day 1 and &lt;a href=&#34;https://goo.gl/maps/ccdwwmcdQRRm1Sb2A&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Maison de la Simulation&lt;/a&gt; for
days 2 and 3.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When&lt;/strong&gt;: 20th-22nd of Septembre 2023.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/e/kokkos-1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;register here!&lt;/a&gt; for day 1.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Neurospin:
&lt;a href=&#34;https://joliot.cea.fr/drf/joliot/Pages/Entites_de_recherche/neurospin/Plan-neurospin.aspx&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;How to come&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d1706.7828375688696!2d2.148987922683708!3d48.72041061301221!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e67f14e80ea87d%3A0x9c50e7a885b66e5d!2sNeurospin!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sfr!4v1690451310534!5m2!1sen!2sfr&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maison de la Simulation:
&lt;a href=&#34;https://mdls.fr/how-to-come/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;How to come&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2631.8449189785!2d2.15407651328232!3d48.72755487119501!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e67f3d6ca35351%3A0xad658a7f81b4a1fe!2sMaison%20de%20la%20Simulation!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sfr!4v1690451425962!5m2!1sen!2sfr&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>CExA Kick-off</title>
      <link>https://cexa-project.org/news/2023-06-01-kickoff/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://cexa-project.org/news/2023-06-01-kickoff/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;CExA will hold its kick-off in Neurospin Amphitheatre on the 19th of Septembre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have always dreamt to start with GPU computing or if you are a Kokkos user and have hit bumps on the road and wonder how CExA can help you, this is the day for you.
This presentation day will be an opportunity to get to know CExA and its environment better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wan to know more, we invite you to stay during the Kokkos training on the following three days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We hope to see you at the event!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://goo.gl/maps/DrqiALxY547iXshJA&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Neurospin Amphitheatre&lt;/a&gt;, how to come: &lt;a href=&#34;https://joliot.cea.fr/drf/joliot/Pages/Entites_de_recherche/neurospin/Plan-neurospin.aspx&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When&lt;/strong&gt;: 19th of Septembre 2023.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/event/10076/timetable/#20230919&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agenda&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d1706.7828375688696!2d2.148987922683708!3d48.72041061301221!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e67f14e80ea87d%3A0x9c50e7a885b66e5d!2sNeurospin!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sfr!4v1690451310534!5m2!1sen!2sfr&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
</description>
